content.htmlText: Close to the famous Arclight Cinemas, Griffith Park, Runyan Canyon, Hollywood Blvd Walk of Stars, Highland Centre, The Palladium, Amoeba Music, Farmers Market on Vine, and more!
Close to the famous Arclight Cinemas, Griffith Park, Runyan Canyon, Hollywood Blvd Walk of Stars, Highland Centre, The Palladium, Amoeba Music, Farmers Market on Vine, and more!

As a guest you have a spot for a vehicle in our private gated driveway. If you don't have a vehicle, there are still plenty of ways to get around such as scooters, Uber, Lyft, a convenient metro stop on Vine & Hollywood Blvd and good ole "heals and toes" ;) Many shops and amenities are within walking distance.

section.title: Things to know
section.houseRulesSubtitle: You'll be staying in someone's home, so please treat it with care and respect.

html.htmlText:
We hope that you will love and respect the home as we do. We keep a very clean home and hope that you will leave it the way that you found it. (Don't worry we will wash the sheets and towels for you. Please just place them in the laundry basket outside your door on your departure.

We also ask our guests to please remove shoes when in the house. There is a spot you can set them next to the door for easy access.

We are a non smoking home and ask that you do not smoke inside the house. You are welcome to use the back porch, the front porch and outdoor spaces to smoke, however. We are 420 friendly :)

Please always lock the back door after coming in at night.

We are not loud, late night partiers and hope that our guests will enjoy their stay in Hollywood, but return home respecting the hosts and any other guests at the house.

Please do not bring anyone who was not on the initial reservation home with you. Safety first. If you would like to invite a guest back to the house, please let us know in advance and we can make exceptions.

There is room for one additional car in the driveway. And unfortunately, no additional animals are allowed. 

Thanks and we can't wait to meet you! :)

htmlDescription.htmlText:
Smack dab in the heart of Hollywood, this charming home and creative oasis is within walking distance of everything interesting and beautiful in Hollywood. Its conveniently located on a private tucked away street providing you privacy, inspiration and convenience! FUN HOLLYWOOD FACTS: this is the former home to a young Marilyn Monroe, and also was the house that the Showtime show, The Real L Word, was filmed. Lots of creative energy and inspiration here!

The space
The room you will be staying in is called Tranquility Room. Set on the back of the house, you will get a lovely view of the garden as the sun comes up to greet you for the day in Los Angeles. This includes a high quality queen size bed with a very comfortable memory foam mattress, streaming flat panel TV with Roku, spacious closet, ceiling fan, and smart device enabled. There is an automated standing / sitting desk in the room to use during your stay. The room is also conveniently located right next to the full guest bathroom. The room also has a smart lock doorknob so you don't have to worry about carrying around keys. We have also included some lovely Los Angeles travel and tour books for you to peruse and get inspired.

As you can see from the pics, there are plenty of delightful plants throughout the home, inside and out, to create a harmonious vibe. Including a bountiful orange tree in the backyard which we harvest often for some fresh OJ!

There is also a laundry room with a full size washer and dryer that you are welcome to use if needed. You will also have access to all the common areas of the main house including the kitchen lounge, living room, oversized full kitchen, guest bathroom and shower as well as a private front patio lounge area, and a back deck outdoor space and lounge area, which we also grow a garden in.

You are also welcome to complimentary fruit, coffee & tea, as well as fruit & herb infused water that we will make available to you during your stay with us!

Guest access
As a guest you have a spot for a vehicle in our private gated driveway in which you will receive a remote control clicker to get in and out. Also, you will be given a pin for the smart locks in the front and back of the house for easy access anytime.

During your stay
Shay & Ginger are available on site for any questions, recommendations, or additional accommodations during your stay :)

Other things to note
Host are fully vaccinated and follow all COVID safety protocols.
There are also furry residents, Juno and Piper, two small and very sweet dogs, that will greet you when you arrive.

License number
HSR22-003545

section.subtitle: AirCover is comprehensive protection included for free with every booking.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.
